                <h1>Derek Jeter: A Legend of Baseball</h1>
                <p>Derek Jeter, the legendary shortstop, is celebrated for his prolific career with the New York Yankees. His clutch performances, five World Series championships, and steadfast leadership made him a beloved sports figure. Jeter's influence extends beyond the field, as he continues to inspire through his philanthropic efforts and business ventures.</p>
